1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,032
<i> ~ Episode 11 ~</i>

2
00:00:04,267 --> 00:00:06,024
But this matter started with you

3
00:00:06,024 --> 00:00:08,525
Ling Rong was never implicated in it

4
00:00:08,525 --> 00:00:11,391
But now she's actually gone to the Cold Palace

5
00:00:11,391 --> 00:00:13,097
to ask that someone be strangled alive

6
00:00:13,097 --> 00:00:16,662
This is completely unlike her

7
00:00:16,662 --> 00:00:18,178
usual gentle and warm self

8
00:00:19,195 --> 00:00:20,920
A frightened rabbit can bite people

9
00:00:21,312 --> 00:00:23,770
But this is a matter that even Su Pei Sheng didn't think to interfere with

10
00:00:23,770 --> 00:00:26,538
yet Ling Rong was able to deal with it so efficiently

11
00:00:26,538 --> 00:00:29,314
I'm too surprised

12
00:00:29,856 --> 00:00:31,049
Although it's surprising,

13
00:00:31,049 --> 00:00:35,382
Ling Rong did it because of us

14
00:00:36,121 --> 00:00:39,552
Though that is true, but I still feel that

15
00:00:40,534 --> 00:00:42,866
it's too unlike the Ling Rong that we know

16
00:00:57,293 --> 00:00:58,283
She's dead?

17
00:00:58,830 --> 00:00:59,790
Utterly and completely so

18
00:01:00,483 --> 00:01:01,970
When she was dragged to the burial site,

19
00:01:01,970 --> 00:01:03,581
someone personally witnessed it

20
00:01:03,581 --> 00:01:05,296
It was done very viciously,

21
00:01:05,296 --> 00:01:07,985
her neck was practically severed. It was frightening!

22
00:01:09,614 --> 00:01:11,284
Those things without their genitals

23
00:01:11,284 --> 00:01:14,283
are still rather efficient in their work

24
00:01:15,708 --> 00:01:16,877
But that's not surprising

25
00:01:16,877 --> 00:01:19,739
She even dared to offend those close to the Emperor

26
00:01:19,739 --> 00:01:21,783
She deserves her ending

27
00:01:23,856 --> 00:01:25,551
Did she reveal anything?

28
00:01:25,551 --> 00:01:26,622
Not one word

29
00:01:28,341 --> 00:01:29,552
At least she was smart enough not to

30
00:01:29,552 --> 00:01:33,065
In the past, I underestimated the sickly Zhen Huan

31
00:01:34,445 --> 00:01:35,892
Now, we'll see

32
00:01:40,228 --> 00:01:42,722
After these stuffy past couple of days,

33
00:01:42,722 --> 00:01:44,532
it's about time that it rains

34
00:01:54,014 --> 00:01:54,938
Jinxi

35
00:02:01,500 --> 00:02:03,953
Mistress, why aren't you sleeping?

36
00:02:04,602 --> 00:02:05,780
I'm quite scared

37
00:02:07,237 --> 00:02:08,623
Those myths and ghost stories

38
00:02:08,623 --> 00:02:10,478
are mere folk tales

39
00:02:10,478 --> 00:02:12,405
Don't take them to heart

40
00:02:13,719 --> 00:02:15,491
I'm not scared of ghost stories

41
00:02:16,887 --> 00:02:18,103
I'm afraid

42
00:02:19,115 --> 00:02:20,775
that although Yushi has passed on

43
00:02:20,775 --> 00:02:24,669
that this matter hasn't been completely resolved

44
00:02:25,675 --> 00:02:27,166
Mistress suspects

45
00:02:27,166 --> 00:02:29,449
that someone was giving Yushi the orders?

46
00:02:30,547 --> 00:02:31,662
Think about it carefully

47
00:02:31,662 --> 00:02:34,275
Yushi isn't a calculative person with deep motives

48
00:02:35,392 --> 00:02:36,969
She was merely a palace maid

49
00:02:36,969 --> 00:02:38,258
how would she know about poisons?

50
00:02:38,258 --> 00:02:41,228
How would she know how much to put in my medicine?

51
00:02:41,228 --> 00:02:42,731
And how would she know how to carry out the deed

52
00:02:42,731 --> 00:02:44,418
by planting people both inside and outside of Palace of Shattered Jade?

53
00:02:44,418 --> 00:02:46,435
Furthermore, where did she get the poison?

54
00:02:46,858 --> 00:02:47,916
You're right

55
00:02:47,916 --> 00:02:51,029
Mistress should have kept her alive

56
00:02:51,029 --> 00:02:52,239
and interrogated her carefully

57
00:02:53,286 --> 00:02:54,481
She hated me to the core

58
00:02:54,481 --> 00:02:56,567
and thus wouldn't have revealed the actual perpetrator

59
00:02:57,596 --> 00:02:59,507
She might even have maligned someone else

60
00:03:01,316 --> 00:03:02,647
But with her death

61
00:03:02,647 --> 00:03:05,026
the person instructing her would relax

62
00:03:05,026 --> 00:03:06,936
and we may use such an opportunity

63
00:03:09,773 --> 00:03:12,349
So we should use Yushi's death

64
00:03:12,349 --> 00:03:14,079
to put up a good performance?

65
00:03:26,998 --> 00:03:28,693
Ghost!

66
00:03:29,424 --> 00:03:30,341
Ghost!

67
00:03:31,457 --> 00:03:33,685
Ghost!

68
00:03:34,989 --> 00:03:36,356
How much longer?

69
00:03:36,356 --> 00:03:37,549
We're almost there

70
00:03:37,549 --> 00:03:39,815
Mistress was at Precious Flower Hall praying for half the night

71
00:03:39,815 --> 00:03:40,916
It's been hard on you

72
00:03:41,855 --> 00:03:43,987
The Empress hasn't been feeling well lately

73
00:03:43,987 --> 00:03:47,085
Praying for her is my duty

74
00:03:55,033 --> 00:03:55,993
Who is crying?

75
00:03:56,590 --> 00:03:58,623
It sounds creepy. Let's go, hurry!

76
00:04:03,678 --> 00:04:04,693
Ghost!

77
00:04:06,298 --> 00:04:08,593
There's a ghost! A ghost!

78
00:04:11,659 --> 00:04:12,850
Ghost!

79
00:04:34,284 --> 00:04:35,450
Did you really see it?

80
00:04:36,955 --> 00:04:39,344
Precious sister was praying for half the night

81
00:04:39,344 --> 00:04:40,462
Maybe you were seeing things?

82
00:04:40,689 --> 00:04:42,682
If you don't believe me, ask Sang'er

83
00:04:43,355 --> 00:04:44,510
She saw it too!

84
00:04:44,959 --> 00:04:47,678
It's true. It had a woman's hair

85
00:04:48,758 --> 00:04:49,871
and was cold and creepy

86
00:04:50,708 --> 00:04:53,203
There was the smell of decay; the smell of a dead person

87
00:04:54,124 --> 00:04:56,855
See? Even Sang'er was scared witless

88
00:04:57,883 --> 00:04:59,963
She's the sharpest maid in my palace

89
00:05:00,835 --> 00:05:01,579
Yes

90
00:05:01,579 --> 00:05:05,455
I heard that a eunuch saw it too

91
00:05:06,280 --> 00:05:07,781
and was scared to the point of sickness

92
00:05:08,435 --> 00:05:09,545
I really saw it

93
00:05:10,220 --> 00:05:13,053
She was in white and had a ghostly pale face

94
00:05:13,762 --> 00:05:17,220
with a tongue this long. She was even bloodied.

95
00:05:18,386 --> 00:05:19,800
Her eyes had blood too

96
00:05:21,036 --> 00:05:25,024
Her hair was a mess and she was crying and crying

97
00:05:25,641 --> 00:05:27,042
She was crying so terribly

98
00:05:27,042 --> 00:05:28,761
Perhaps she was a woman who died grievously

99
00:05:29,403 --> 00:05:30,836
You usually don't say much

100
00:05:30,836 --> 00:05:32,447
but now you've hit the nail on the head

101
00:05:32,447 --> 00:05:35,302
If it weren't a woman who died grievously, would she be crying at night?

102
00:05:36,120 --> 00:05:37,144
A woman who died grievously?

103
00:05:39,977 --> 00:05:44,354
It must be Yushi who died in the Cold Palace

104
00:05:44,354 --> 00:05:46,142
It must be Yushi's ghost who has come to seek vengeance

105
00:05:46,677 --> 00:05:49,166
Don't talk rubbish. She was properly convicted.

106
00:05:49,166 --> 00:05:50,065
What grievances could she have?

107
00:05:50,065 --> 00:05:51,991
What do you know?

108
00:05:51,991 --> 00:05:54,673
At that time she didn't want to die

109
00:05:54,673 --> 00:05:56,581
so Eunuch Su couldn't complete his job

110
00:05:56,581 --> 00:05:59,906
She ended up being strangled to death

111
00:06:01,456 --> 00:06:04,430
That back palace is so chaotic<br><br>Why don't we

112
00:06:04,430 --> 00:06:06,009
wait for His Majesty to return and inform him then?

113
00:06:06,337 --> 00:06:08,192
His Majesty hates ghost stories and superstitions

114
00:06:08,192 --> 00:06:10,406
If you dare to, then you go and tell him

115
00:06:11,497 --> 00:06:13,832
A person's grievance must go to the person who caused it <br>I didn't do anything to her!

116
00:06:13,832 --> 00:06:15,500
Why would she come and look for me?

117
00:06:15,677 --> 00:06:17,814
That's why she didn't harm you

118
00:06:17,814 --> 00:06:19,394
Didn't she leave immediately?

119
00:06:19,394 --> 00:06:21,736
Otherwise, would you still be sitting here alive?

120
00:06:22,588 --> 00:06:25,149
Then who would she look for?

121
00:06:26,766 --> 00:06:28,207
Anyway, it has nothing to do with Sister Smiles

122
00:06:32,284 --> 00:06:33,820
I heard that after Yushi's death

123
00:06:33,820 --> 00:06:36,572
Precious Smiles hasn't slept well

124
00:06:36,572 --> 00:06:38,161
so the physician has gone to check on her

125
00:06:38,161 --> 00:06:39,348
Thank you for your concern

126
00:06:39,348 --> 00:06:41,696
Physician Wen is looking after her

127
00:06:42,490 --> 00:06:45,472
But she hasn't seen improvement

128
00:06:46,537 --> 00:06:48,860
The palace has been running rampant with ghosts these past couple of days

129
00:06:48,860 --> 00:06:50,703
More than ten people have seen it

130
00:06:50,703 --> 00:06:53,257
It's hard to get a good night's rest

131
00:06:53,826 --> 00:06:56,432
I heard so too. Some eunuchs have even fallen ill

132
00:06:56,432 --> 00:06:59,183
Precious Fucha doesn't even dare to leave her rooms

133
00:06:59,183 --> 00:07:00,254
The Emperor has said

134
00:07:00,254 --> 00:07:04,325
that ghost stories stem from people's overactive imagination

135
00:07:05,572 --> 00:07:07,405
Furthermore, so many people have seen it

136
00:07:07,405 --> 00:07:10,566
they're merely adding their own dimensions to the tale

137
00:07:11,610 --> 00:07:14,001
It looks like Princess of Regularity hasn't seen His Majesty in so long

138
00:07:14,001 --> 00:07:16,174
that she's even forgotten his words

139
00:07:16,617 --> 00:07:18,822
Niang niang often hears the Emperor's words of wisdom and is therefore unafraid

140
00:07:18,822 --> 00:07:21,442
unlike us who seldom see His Majesty

141
00:07:22,238 --> 00:07:24,536
If all of us have His Majesty's wisdom with us,

142
00:07:24,536 --> 00:07:26,483
then the palace would naturally have less of these rumours

143
00:07:28,295 --> 00:07:31,215
Unfortunately, we're not so blessed

144
00:07:32,592 --> 00:07:35,024
Since you're not blessed, then you should pray for more blessings

145
00:07:35,723 --> 00:07:37,764
Otherwise, when the grieving ghost comes upon you

146
00:07:37,764 --> 00:07:39,297
it'll be too late to pray to the gods

147
00:07:40,679 --> 00:07:44,091
All of you talk about such ugly things in private,

148
00:07:44,091 --> 00:07:46,467
talking about nonsensical ghosts and supernatural demons

149
00:07:46,705 --> 00:07:48,182
I don't believe it

150
00:07:48,961 --> 00:07:50,420
Yushi will naturally look for

151
00:07:50,420 --> 00:07:52,250
whoever she hated while she was alive

152
00:07:52,250 --> 00:07:54,718
Why is everyone else even feeling worried?

153
00:07:55,492 --> 00:07:56,761
Niang niang's teachings are right

154
00:07:56,761 --> 00:07:58,581
Yushi was not receiving orders from anyone

155
00:07:58,581 --> 00:08:01,028
of course she was acting out of her own evil thoughts

156
00:08:01,888 --> 00:08:03,622
If someone were instructing her behind the scenes,

157
00:08:03,622 --> 00:08:06,838
she'd definitely go and haunt that person whom caused her death

158
00:08:06,838 --> 00:08:09,640
and ask that person why she had to be the scapegoat

159
00:08:38,648 --> 00:08:40,353
Your Highness looks much better now

160
00:08:43,010 --> 00:08:44,228
Today is the first day of the month

161
00:08:44,228 --> 00:08:46,137
it is my duty to make offerings to the gods

162
00:08:47,007 --> 00:08:50,155
and obtain their protection. Naturally, I feel better.

163
00:08:50,974 --> 00:08:52,565
Your Highness was sick for two days and may not know

164
00:08:53,023 --> 00:08:57,473
but rumours are running amok in the back palace <br><br>about ghosts and the supernatural

165
00:08:57,940 --> 00:08:59,950
Rumours should not be believed in

166
00:08:59,950 --> 00:09:02,518
The Forbidden City has stood for hundreds of years

167
00:09:02,518 --> 00:09:04,344
what kinds of supernatural tales have not been heard before?

168
00:09:04,344 --> 00:09:07,130
If there is really a problem, then an exorcism should be arranged

169
00:09:08,338 --> 00:09:09,547
Once the exorcism is performed,

170
00:09:09,547 --> 00:09:12,535
wouldn't the back palace strengthen their belief in the supernatural?

171
00:09:12,897 --> 00:09:15,438
Performing an exorcism is not about belief

172
00:09:15,438 --> 00:09:17,527
but to put everyone's minds at ease

173
00:09:18,150 --> 00:09:21,241
Then get the Precious Flower Temple's priest to perform the rites

174
00:09:21,241 --> 00:09:23,764
Performing an big exorcism

175
00:09:25,045 --> 00:09:28,776
The Cold Place is so spooky

176
00:09:28,776 --> 00:09:31,026
I'll ask the priest

177
00:09:31,026 --> 00:09:33,466
to release souls from purgatory in the Cold Place

178
00:09:43,138 --> 00:09:45,041
I was in a trance the days before

179
00:09:45,041 --> 00:09:46,450
I thank Niangniang's kindness

180
00:09:46,450 --> 00:09:48,306
for exempting me giving respects in those days.

181
00:09:48,635 --> 00:09:50,524
You look much better now

182
00:09:51,046 --> 00:09:53,237
Several days ago when I looked at your face

183
00:09:53,237 --> 00:09:54,327
it was so pale

184
00:09:54,922 --> 00:09:56,308
Thank you for Empress's concern

185
00:09:56,308 --> 00:09:58,636
I should have payed respects to Niang Niang

186
00:09:58,636 --> 00:10:01,526
please forgive me

187
00:10:01,998 --> 00:10:02,956
Sit down

188
00:10:03,338 --> 00:10:04,188
Thank you Niang Niang

189
00:10:05,693 --> 00:10:07,181
You were not so well

190
00:10:07,181 --> 00:10:09,463
if you came here everyday

191
00:10:09,463 --> 00:10:11,561
I'll be worried

192
00:10:12,785 --> 00:10:15,997
Right, it's ok for you to come in the daytime

193
00:10:15,997 --> 00:10:17,650
but if at night

194
00:10:17,650 --> 00:10:19,699
and see some ghosts

195
00:10:19,699 --> 00:10:21,434
that's too bad

196
00:10:24,836 --> 00:10:27,322
Your Highness, the thunder is so loud

197
00:10:27,322 --> 00:10:30,079
I'm afraid that there will be a thunderstorm later

198
00:10:31,128 --> 00:10:33,712
It has indeed been raining for the past two days, making it inconvenient to go out

199
00:10:33,712 --> 00:10:36,516
It's not early, all of you should return

200
00:10:38,420 --> 00:10:39,982
We take our leave

201
00:10:47,855 --> 00:10:49,578
Why isn't Precious Cao here today?

202
00:10:50,085 --> 00:10:52,478
Princess Wen Yi caught a cold and she had to accompany her

203
00:10:52,478 --> 00:10:53,815
thus she wasn't able to come out

204
00:10:57,742 --> 00:10:58,838
Respectfully send off Princess of Glory

205
00:10:59,987 --> 00:11:01,413
Respectfully send off Pin of Beauty

206
00:11:01,413 --> 00:11:02,991
Even though Precious Smiles is feeling better,

207
00:11:02,991 --> 00:11:05,860
but I think you look very frail

208
00:11:05,860 --> 00:11:09,424
The feeling of having nightmares keep you up must be horrible

209
00:11:09,424 --> 00:11:10,497
Niang niang, please stop

210
00:11:10,497 --> 00:11:13,001
That thing is heinous, it will haunt people

211
00:11:13,001 --> 00:11:15,280
You've really been scared witless

212
00:11:15,280 --> 00:11:18,300
You even dare to spout nonsense before me

213
00:11:18,994 --> 00:11:20,381
Please forgive her Princess of Glory

214
00:11:20,381 --> 00:11:23,261
Jiejie is indeed frightened by the incident

215
00:11:23,261 --> 00:11:25,004
It really is...

216
00:11:27,304 --> 00:11:29,303
There've just been too many people who have seen it

217
00:11:29,303 --> 00:11:31,814
so it's best to be careful

218
00:11:31,814 --> 00:11:34,190
Yes, exactly! I saw it myself!

219
00:11:34,190 --> 00:11:36,256
If there really isn't a ghost with grievances

220
00:11:36,256 --> 00:11:39,039
then why is the Empress arranging an exorcism?

221
00:11:39,039 --> 00:11:41,405
That ghost is full of such anger and grief,

222
00:11:41,405 --> 00:11:44,499
I wonder if the priest handling the rites will be powerful enough to exorcise her

223
00:11:45,302 --> 00:11:46,294
Can a priest be unable to do so?

224
00:11:46,965 --> 00:11:49,630
She died so horribly. Her grievances must be deep.

225
00:11:50,467 --> 00:11:54,434
It is said while the priest climbs a foot, the devil climbs ten

226
00:11:55,029 --> 00:11:56,569
I heard that His Majesty granted Yushi death by sucide

227
00:11:56,569 --> 00:11:58,780
but the concubines that were close to her

228
00:11:58,780 --> 00:12:00,476
didn't do a single thing to plead for her

229
00:12:00,476 --> 00:12:04,125
that's why she died so horribly in the Cold Palace

230
00:12:04,676 --> 00:12:06,117
These words from the servants' mouths

231
00:12:06,117 --> 00:12:07,409
can be left alone

232
00:12:07,409 --> 00:12:10,035
But from the mouths of you ladies

233
00:12:10,035 --> 00:12:12,317
is a show of lack of dignity and grace

234
00:12:12,468 --> 00:12:14,439
These words should indeed not be uttered

235
00:12:14,439 --> 00:12:17,432
But everyone is scared and uneasy now

236
00:12:17,432 --> 00:12:19,925
I heard Precious Cao has never been a timid one

237
00:12:19,925 --> 00:12:21,828
if she were here we would feel better

238
00:12:21,828 --> 00:12:24,654
But why is it that Precious Cao isn't here today?

239
00:12:25,195 --> 00:12:27,017
Princess Wen Yi caught a cold

240
00:12:27,017 --> 00:12:28,535
Precious Cao has to look after her

241
00:12:28,535 --> 00:12:30,796
That's why she isn't here to pay her respects to the Empress

242
00:12:31,490 --> 00:12:33,606
Precious Smiles has always been a thoughtful person

243
00:12:33,606 --> 00:12:35,309
I'm sure you're thinking too much right now

244
00:12:36,941 --> 00:12:37,794
Let's go

245
00:12:37,794 --> 00:12:39,812
That's true, as long as our conscience is clear

246
00:12:39,812 --> 00:12:41,392
we shouldn't be scared of having ghosts on our doorsteps

247
00:13:00,199 --> 00:13:01,256
Hurry up, let's go

248
00:13:01,256 --> 00:13:02,828
It's already so dark outside

249
00:13:02,828 --> 00:13:04,559
Any later and the unclean things will start coming out

250
00:13:04,559 --> 00:13:06,004
Yes, it's almost night

251
00:13:06,004 --> 00:13:07,237
we should leave quickly

252
00:13:23,793 --> 00:13:25,103
What is that?

253
00:13:25,555 --> 00:13:26,589
What's the matter?

254
00:13:26,589 --> 00:13:28,307
- What is that? <br> - What happened?

255
00:13:39,657 --> 00:13:42,070
Ghost!

256
00:13:42,614 --> 00:13:46,793
She came. The ghost came to get me!

257
00:13:48,140 --> 00:13:49,176
That's Li Pin's voice

258
00:13:49,176 --> 00:13:49,980
Yes

259
00:13:49,980 --> 00:13:51,633
Jin Xi, quickly report this to the Empress

260
00:13:51,633 --> 00:13:52,735
Yes

261
00:13:52,735 --> 00:13:54,304
Hurry, let's go take a look

262
00:14:03,037 --> 00:14:06,265
- Ghost! <br> - It's the middle of the night

263
00:14:06,265 --> 00:14:07,416
What are you crying madly about?

264
00:14:07,416 --> 00:14:09,072
Quickly shut your mouth

265
00:14:09,317 --> 00:14:11,583
Ghost!

266
00:14:11,583 --> 00:14:13,644
She came. She came, didn't she?

267
00:14:13,644 --> 00:14:14,748
She came, didn't she?

