00:27:01,572 --> 00:27:03,057
Emperor arrives

535
00:27:04,600 --> 00:27:06,645
Your Majesty

536
00:27:06,645 --> 00:27:07,825
Quickly get up

537
00:27:08,509 --> 00:27:09,713
Your Majesty, you're finally back

538
00:27:09,713 --> 00:27:10,884
Sit

539
00:27:14,713 --> 00:27:15,577
Miss me?

540
00:27:16,827 --> 00:27:17,858
I miss Your Majesty

541
00:27:17,858 --> 00:27:20,434
You must be very tired for your inspection tour?

542
00:27:20,975 --> 00:27:22,823
I just went to see the Empress Dowager

543
00:27:22,823 --> 00:27:25,100
The poisoning incident has ended

544
00:27:25,100 --> 00:27:28,945
You can now rest assured. I can also sigh in relief.

545
00:27:29,608 --> 00:27:31,935
Since the incident is already over, Your Majesty need not be angry about it anymore

546
00:27:31,935 --> 00:27:35,102
Pin of Beauty only resents me

547
00:27:35,102 --> 00:27:36,933
because she cares about Your Majesty.

548
00:27:37,911 --> 00:27:38,990
Cares about me?

549
00:27:38,990 --> 00:27:41,586
Does she care about me or her own glory?

550
00:27:41,586 --> 00:27:43,345
Only she really knows

551
00:27:44,206 --> 00:27:45,709
Even if she really cares about me,

552
00:27:45,709 --> 00:27:47,928
doing something so sinister

553
00:27:47,928 --> 00:27:50,097
is absolutely unforgiveable.

554
00:27:50,666 --> 00:27:52,694
Pin of Beauty made a mistake. She has already been punished.

555
00:27:53,680 --> 00:27:55,172
Although Princess of Glory

556
00:27:55,172 --> 00:27:57,030
usually hangs around Pin of Beauty,

557
00:27:57,030 --> 00:28:00,729
she wouldn't be so stupid

558
00:28:00,729 --> 00:28:02,257
as to be complicit in this matter.

559
00:28:02,257 --> 00:28:06,596
Princess of Glory is blessed and has a resolute mind

560
00:28:06,983 --> 00:28:09,810
Resolute? What do you mean by resolute?

561
00:28:11,334 --> 00:28:13,692
Doing things with resolve and firmness, knows how to handle matters and people

562
00:28:13,692 --> 00:28:14,924
That is what being resolute means

563
00:28:15,664 --> 00:28:17,133
Princess of Glory assists in managing the inner palace

564
00:28:17,133 --> 00:28:19,278
She should be worthy of these two words

565
00:28:19,933 --> 00:28:21,336
Everything has two sides

566
00:28:22,248 --> 00:28:24,394
Empress Dowager has always used proper judgment in handling affairs

567
00:28:24,394 --> 00:28:26,628
She never meddles in matters of the inner palace

568
00:28:26,628 --> 00:28:28,507
But if she gets involved,

569
00:28:28,507 --> 00:28:30,903
it must be something major that she cannot tolerate.

570
00:28:31,894 --> 00:28:35,304
This time around, it is a warning to the back palace

571
00:28:35,304 --> 00:28:37,834
not to cause such pandemonium again

572
00:28:39,248 --> 00:28:42,855
I just hope that from now on, everyone in the inner palace

573
00:28:42,855 --> 00:28:45,272
can be more considerate of each other, and not so resentful.

574
00:28:45,272 --> 00:28:48,053
Only that way can Your Majesty concentrate on affairs of state

575
00:28:48,053 --> 00:28:49,305
without fear of trouble back home.

576
00:28:55,536 --> 00:28:58,292
This morning at court I saw your father cough a bit

577
00:28:58,292 --> 00:28:59,977
He seems to have caught a cold

578
00:29:01,289 --> 00:29:02,466
Father has always had laryngitis

579
00:29:02,466 --> 00:29:04,485
I'm also very worried

580
00:29:05,365 --> 00:29:06,737
So after court,

581
00:29:06,737 --> 00:29:08,150
I had Su Pei Sheng

582
00:29:08,150 --> 00:29:10,650
get two bottles of honey loquat syrup for your father.

583
00:29:12,034 --> 00:29:12,972
Many thanks Your Majesty

584
00:29:14,888 --> 00:29:17,585
He's your father. I should show care for him.

585
00:29:20,258 --> 00:29:21,216
Father's laryngitis

586
00:29:21,216 --> 00:29:23,746
is something that mother worries about everyday.

587
00:29:23,746 --> 00:29:25,921
She cooks almond lily in the spring

588
00:29:25,921 --> 00:29:27,768
and Sichuan fritillary bulb and pears in the Autumn

589
00:29:27,768 --> 00:29:29,694
she has taken care of him for many years

590
00:29:31,197 --> 00:29:32,741
Your parents care deeply for each other

591
00:29:34,028 --> 00:29:37,228
which is why their daughter is so gentle and affectionate.

592
00:29:38,712 --> 00:29:40,073
Your Majesty jokes with me

593
00:29:44,587 --> 00:29:48,468
Mother, today is your death anniversary

594
00:29:50,099 --> 00:29:52,542
I don't know whether dad still remembers this or not

595
00:29:54,233 --> 00:29:55,455
whether just as me

596
00:29:57,364 --> 00:29:59,410
I can only burn the ghost money for you secretly

597
00:30:01,772 --> 00:30:02,841
Mother

598
00:30:02,841 --> 00:30:04,649
daughter is unfilial

599
00:30:06,402 --> 00:30:08,527
I don't know

600
00:30:10,065 --> 00:30:11,533
when I can stand out among people

601
00:30:13,701 --> 00:30:16,332
and burn the ghost money for you aboveboard

602
00:30:26,268 --> 00:30:27,784
So late, who is still there

603
00:30:38,401 --> 00:30:39,233
How dare you

604
00:30:39,805 --> 00:30:41,718
how dare you burn the ghost money in the Royal Palaces

605
00:30:42,587 --> 00:30:43,423
Precious Cao

606
00:30:44,324 --> 00:30:46,774
You, you are Precious Smile's maid?

607
00:30:49,841 --> 00:30:50,852
You know

608
00:30:50,852 --> 00:30:53,661
the ominous thing is forbiden in the palaces

609
00:30:53,661 --> 00:30:55,578
Burning ghost money is even more serious

610
00:30:56,368 --> 00:30:59,006
Precious Smile couldn't save you even if she knows

611
00:30:59,540 --> 00:31:01,566
Forgive me Precious Cao, servant will never do it again

612
00:31:01,566 --> 00:31:03,595
please don't tell young mistress

613
00:31:04,139 --> 00:31:05,715
Alright, stand up

614
00:31:06,242 --> 00:31:07,314
Please forgive me

615
00:31:09,767 --> 00:31:11,382
You're lucky that I was the one who found you.

616
00:31:12,078 --> 00:31:13,293
if it was anyone else

617
00:31:13,293 --> 00:31:14,724
they would take you to Bureau of Cautious Punishment already

618
00:31:15,852 --> 00:31:16,824
tell me the truth

619
00:31:16,824 --> 00:31:18,335
why you burned it here

620
00:31:20,284 --> 00:31:21,648
Today is my mother's death anniversary

621
00:31:24,476 --> 00:31:25,873
You are filial

622
00:31:27,153 --> 00:31:28,407
but since you are doing it for your mother

623
00:31:28,407 --> 00:31:30,748
Why did you burn it here

624
00:31:30,748 --> 00:31:32,028
instead of in Palace of Shattered Jade

625
00:31:33,274 --> 00:31:34,104
Servant dare not

626
00:31:34,338 --> 00:31:35,691
You are most loved

627
00:31:35,691 --> 00:31:37,304
by your Precious Smile

628
00:31:37,304 --> 00:31:39,232
even your food and clothes are different from others

629
00:31:40,299 --> 00:31:43,574
why didn't she help you with your filial piety

630
00:31:47,678 --> 00:31:49,641
Servant was afraid of offending young mistress

631
00:31:52,099 --> 00:31:53,386
please don't tell young mistress

632
00:31:53,386 --> 00:31:55,136
about what happened today

633
00:31:55,943 --> 00:31:56,984
I know

634
00:31:58,212 --> 00:31:59,707
sweep away all the ashes quickly

635
00:31:59,707 --> 00:32:02,333
they will catch you if they find the ashes

636
00:32:03,308 --> 00:32:04,314
Thank Precious

637
00:32:11,854 --> 00:32:14,166
Precious Flower Hall's priest has done four rites

638
00:32:14,166 --> 00:32:17,251
total expenses on joss sticks and candles is 1800 taels

639
00:32:18,016 --> 00:32:19,285
It's getting hot

640
00:32:19,285 --> 00:32:21,905
Every maid and eunuch in the palaces

641
00:32:21,905 --> 00:32:24,251
have been given green bean soup at lunch to clear their heat

642
00:32:24,251 --> 00:32:27,692
This costs 32 taels per day

643
00:32:28,583 --> 00:32:29,466
Wait

644
00:32:30,548 --> 00:32:32,754
One day's green bean soup is 32 taels?

645
00:32:32,754 --> 00:32:34,646
Then what about a month's worth?

646
00:32:36,807 --> 00:32:41,938
960 taels

647
00:32:43,112 --> 00:32:46,422
Wealth comes from the simple places. <br><br>Although it's just one bowl of green bean soup

648
00:32:46,422 --> 00:32:48,526
but carried out over a long period of time,

649
00:32:48,526 --> 00:32:50,199
it's no small sum

650
00:32:50,709 --> 00:32:51,774
Empress is right

651
00:32:52,870 --> 00:32:56,943
But this has been going on since the previous Emperor's reign

652
00:32:57,924 --> 00:32:59,244
If it was suddenly discontinued,

653
00:32:59,244 --> 00:33:02,623
I'm afraid that there will be grumblings

654
00:33:03,526 --> 00:33:04,789
His Majesty is right

655
00:33:04,789 --> 00:33:06,316
Acts of benevolence from the masters

656
00:33:06,316 --> 00:33:08,528
encourage the servants to do their jobs to the best of their abilities

657
00:33:08,528 --> 00:33:10,910
So this sum of money is not something we should scrimp on

658
00:33:11,603 --> 00:33:13,615
Precious Smiles, what do you think?

659
00:33:14,882 --> 00:33:15,984
I don't understand these things

660
00:33:16,778 --> 00:33:18,226
Mei Jiejie is doing the accounts

661
00:33:18,226 --> 00:33:20,414
So I can only drink my tea

662
00:33:21,283 --> 00:33:23,082
That is the most fortunate lifestyle to have

663
00:33:24,203 --> 00:33:26,662
Your Majesty, I was thinking

664
00:33:26,662 --> 00:33:29,930
that the daily stipend of each palace is never used up

665
00:33:30,618 --> 00:33:32,673
For example, for Precious ladies

666
00:33:33,312 --> 00:33:35,591
they are given 1 sheng and 2 he of rice evey day

667
00:33:35,591 --> 00:33:38,318
6 jin of pork, and 6 jin of fresh vegetables

668
00:33:38,318 --> 00:33:41,939
2 jin of white noodles, 1 jin and 8 liang of tofu...

669
00:33:41,939 --> 00:33:44,321
No matter how they eat, they will never finish eating such large amounts

670
00:33:44,321 --> 00:33:47,253
Not to mention the amount of food delivered to the Pin ladies and the Princesses

671
00:33:47,253 --> 00:33:50,473
I was thinking, why don't we

672
00:33:50,473 --> 00:33:53,229
cut down on the amount of food in exchange for silver for each palace

673
00:33:53,229 --> 00:33:55,303
Then the green bean and ice candy cases

674
00:33:55,303 --> 00:33:58,231
can also be stopped in exchange for money given to the servants

675
00:33:58,231 --> 00:34:00,430
On one hand, we save on money spent,

676
00:34:00,430 --> 00:34:02,590
on the other, everyone gets a share

677
00:34:02,590 --> 00:34:05,562
So that there won't be any cases of

678
00:34:05,562 --> 00:34:08,262
quibbles over someone eating someone else's share and breeding discontent

679
00:34:08,879 --> 00:34:10,028
Jiejie is bright and intelligent

680
00:34:10,028 --> 00:34:11,878
If it were me,

681
00:34:11,878 --> 00:34:13,637
I would never be able to calculate all of that

682
00:34:15,211 --> 00:34:16,300
I have a headache now

683
00:34:16,963 --> 00:34:19,899
Thank goodness Precious Shen is around to do the calculations

684
00:34:20,497 --> 00:34:21,941
What do I know?

685
00:34:21,941 --> 00:34:24,418
If it weren't for the Empress' pointers and teachings,

686
00:34:24,418 --> 00:34:27,258
I would have become the laughingstock of many by now

687
00:34:28,212 --> 00:34:31,290
You're still young, you should practice more

688
00:34:32,351 --> 00:34:37,107
But even practicing will be useless without some kind of natural talent

689
00:34:38,394 --> 00:34:41,591
You must be referring to me then, as someone naturally stupid

690
00:34:43,370 --> 00:34:44,678
Look at her mouth

691
00:34:45,308 --> 00:34:46,526
She still calls herself stupid

692
00:34:47,653 --> 00:34:48,977
Then everyone else must be worse off

693
00:34:49,457 --> 00:34:51,730
In my opinion, Your Majesty cannot blame Meimei

694
00:34:52,574 --> 00:34:54,253
Your Majesty should blame yourself

695
00:34:54,253 --> 00:34:55,845
for having spoilt Meimei's mouth

696
00:34:55,845 --> 00:34:59,312
to the point that it will say whatever it wishes to say

697
00:35:11,954 --> 00:35:14,334
Your servant respectfully greets Princess of Glory

698
00:35:14,334 --> 00:35:15,137
Rise

699
00:35:15,687 --> 00:35:16,464
Thank you, Niang Niang

700
00:35:17,095 --> 00:35:19,898
Go and inform the Empress that I am here to pay my respects

701
00:35:21,426 --> 00:35:24,622
What's wrong? You aren't even going to listen to Niang niang's orders?

702
00:35:24,622 --> 00:35:27,696
Then you don't have to inform her. I'll just go in myself.

703
00:35:28,739 --> 00:35:32,084
Niang Niang. The Empress' illness is acting up

704
00:35:32,084 --> 00:35:33,267
She's ill-disposed to entertain guests

705
00:35:34,230 --> 00:35:36,084
It's precisely because her illness is acting up

706
00:35:36,084 --> 00:35:37,618
that I am here to pay my respects

707
00:35:42,989 --> 00:35:45,231
Niang Niang's illness is acting up, but her spirits seem to be high

708
00:35:45,941 --> 00:35:48,034
His Majesty has come to visit Niang Niang

709
00:35:48,674 --> 00:35:51,315
That's good. Then I'll pay my respects to the Emperor at the same time

710
00:35:52,038 --> 00:35:53,903
That will save me a trip to the Palace of Resting Soul

711
00:35:54,566 --> 00:35:55,715
Niang Niang be at peace,

712
00:35:56,866 --> 00:35:59,856
whether or not the Empress is ill-disposed,

713
00:35:59,856 --> 00:36:01,022
is inconsequential

714
00:36:01,022 --> 00:36:03,822
The important point is whether the Emperor, upon seeing Niang Niang

715
00:36:03,822 --> 00:36:06,645
will get angry and affect his health

716
00:36:07,432 --> 00:36:08,707
Niang Niang is an intelligent person

717
00:36:08,707 --> 00:36:11,482
and thus naturally knows how important the Emperor's regard is

718
00:36:11,482 --> 00:36:14,651
Why do you want to anger the Emperor?

719
00:36:24,147 --> 00:36:25,814
Respectfully sends off Niang Niang

720
00:36:35,684 --> 00:36:38,122
Reporting to Niang Niang, Precious Cao is here

721
00:36:45,960 --> 00:36:47,008
Greetings, Niang Niang

722
00:36:52,373 --> 00:36:55,696
In this summer's heat, it's unsurprising that Niang Niang has fire in her heart

723
00:36:55,696 --> 00:36:57,563
As long as that fire can be dispelled,

724
00:36:57,563 --> 00:36:59,449
I am willing to accept all consequences

725
00:37:00,615 --> 00:37:01,827
Back then you were merely a

726
00:37:01,827 --> 00:37:03,228
poor concubine candidate

727
00:37:03,886 --> 00:37:05,357
Your nameplate was saved and sent to the Duke's abode

728
00:37:05,357 --> 00:37:06,672
You never even got to see the Emperor

729
00:37:07,337 --> 00:37:09,414
If it weren't for me who suggested that you serve the Emperor,

730
00:37:09,414 --> 00:37:12,013
would you have the opportunity to give birth to the princess and become a Precious?

731
00:37:13,522 --> 00:37:15,497
Now that Pin of Beauty and myself are in trouble,

732
00:37:15,497 --> 00:37:18,001
you come up with foul ideas and mess up everything

733
00:37:18,001 --> 00:37:20,514
Yet you have the cheek to say such things before me?

734
00:37:21,442 --> 00:37:22,824
I am not sure what I did wrong

735
00:37:22,824 --> 00:37:24,471
Please tell me

736
00:37:24,471 --> 00:37:26,145
I will make amends for it

737
00:37:27,460 --> 00:37:28,785
I listened to you

738
00:37:29,771 --> 00:37:32,240
and informed the Empress Dowager about Pin of Beauty's madness

739
00:37:32,240 --> 00:37:34,165
so that I will not be implicated

740
00:37:35,092 --> 00:37:36,853
It's fine if Pin of Beauty is sent to the Cold Palace

741
00:37:37,621 --> 00:37:39,682
but I've lost the power to manage the six palaces

742
00:37:40,747 --> 00:37:42,597
All because you thought you were all that

743
00:37:42,597 --> 00:37:43,818
and came up with that plan

744
00:37:45,679 --> 00:37:48,258
Congratulations, Niang Niang

745
00:37:50,243 --> 00:37:53,540
Tell me why I should be congratulated

746
00:37:54,516 --> 00:37:57,270
No matter what Pin of Beauty says, it is only a madwoman's words

747
00:37:57,270 --> 00:37:59,396
No matter how suspicious the Empress Dowager and Emperor are,

748
00:37:59,396 --> 00:38:00,825
they have no evidence to back it up

749
00:38:00,825 --> 00:38:02,928
Although you appear to have lost power,

750
00:38:02,928 --> 00:38:04,426
Niang Niang is able to be safe

751
00:38:04,426 --> 00:38:08,492
Furthermore, the Emperor is a sentimental man

752
00:38:08,492 --> 00:38:11,529
gaining and losing power is entirely within a single thought

753
00:38:11,856 --> 00:38:12,912
You certainly make it sound easy

754
00:38:13,956 --> 00:38:15,832
Now Precious Smiles has wormed her way into the Emperor's heart

755
00:38:15,832 --> 00:38:18,474
The Empress' manipulations are also at work

756
00:38:18,474 --> 00:38:22,175
Now it's so difficult for me to even see the Emperor!

757
00:38:22,722 --> 00:38:23,916
Niang Niang is virtuous

758
00:38:23,916 --> 00:38:26,934
I am willing to do anything for Niang Niang

759
00:38:26,934 --> 00:38:28,058
and provide any advice

760
00:38:28,058 --> 00:38:29,160
What makes you fit?

761
00:38:31,588 --> 00:38:33,048
The Emperor is an affectionate and sentimental man

762
00:38:33,048 --> 00:38:35,403
He dotes on Wen Yi very much

763
00:38:44,295 --> 00:38:46,109
Get up <br><br> Get her a seat

764
00:38:46,682 --> 00:38:48,006
Thank you, Niang Niang

765
00:38:55,814 --> 00:38:58,522
Pin of Beauty is like an embroidered flower - Good to look at, but not very useful

766
00:38:59,187 --> 00:39:01,837
It looks like you're a lot better

767
00:39:02,495 --> 00:39:04,296
You have a daughter to rely on

768
00:39:05,267 --> 00:39:08,630
Unlike me who has no children

769
00:39:09,116 --> 00:39:11,686
I am useless, without Niang Niang's protection,

770
00:39:11,686 --> 00:39:13,536
how can my Princess grow up peacefully?

771
00:39:13,536 --> 00:39:15,830
Niang Niang has always doted on Wen Yi

772
00:39:15,830 --> 00:39:17,490
When Wen Yi is older,

773
00:39:17,490 --> 00:39:19,921
she will look to you as her mother and be filial to you

774
00:39:19,921 --> 00:39:21,365
Look at you

775
00:39:21,365 --> 00:39:23,775
your hair is a mess yet you're still talking to me

776
00:39:25,081 --> 00:39:25,992
It's been hard on you

777
00:39:26,499 --> 00:39:27,614
Song Zhi

778
00:39:27,614 --> 00:39:28,317
Yes

779
00:39:28,317 --> 00:39:30,448
Bring Precious Cao to the back to comb her hair and change her clothes

780
00:39:31,320 --> 00:39:32,167
Yes

781
00:39:33,685 --> 00:39:35,258
Thank you, Niang Niang

782
00:39:35,732 --> 00:39:38,185
The Emperor hasn't seen Wen Yi for a couple of days, right?

783
00:39:38,968 --> 00:39:42,769
Bring Wen Yi to Palace of Benevolent Hope to pay her respects to the Emperor

784
00:39:43,289 --> 00:39:46,565
Yes <br><br>Except that I am not good with words

785
00:39:46,565 --> 00:39:48,576
and I'm afraid that I'll annoy the Emperor

786
00:39:49,238 --> 00:39:51,074
It's all right if you're not good with words

787
00:39:51,757 --> 00:39:53,935
It's enough that Wen Yi knows how to garner his attention

788
00:39:55,028 --> 00:39:56,101
At my dressing table,

789
00:39:56,101 --> 00:39:58,279
there is a phoenix wears herbaceous peony of step-shake

